    <div class="col-sm-6 item-8">
      <div class="aligner">
        <div class="aligner-item">
          And once they no longer needed to travel between SF and NYC to see one another, they discovered they loved to eat and travel together.
          Harry Potter World, New Orleans, Iceland, London, Amsterdam, Rome, Scotland, and so many more, the two grew more in love with each new adventure (and delicious meal).
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 item-7">
      <div class="our-story-image-container">
        <div id="cover-image">
            <img class="cover-image-item" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/huttle/image/upload/a_0/v1513914464/IMG_4104_bwwcu0.jpg">
        </div>
