          After two years in New York together, Chris and Alicia moved back to the Bay Area to start the next chapter of their life, and on July 1st, 2017, Chris proposed to Alicia in the home they built together.
          And, now they're looking forward to being wed on August 11th, 2018 surrounded by their friends and family.
